title: Steelers Drama, NFL Combine Tales with Brady Quinn (Football 2/21)
description:
Will Brinson and Brady Quinn break down the latest news from around the league including the Steelers announcement they won't be franchise tag/transition tagging Le'Veon Bell as well as the Steelers confirmation on their plan to trade Antonio Brown. Then the guys dive into some NFL combine discussion.
